reviewText: I am already giving this " prequel"  5 Stars because I loved " High School Reunion" . Sound stupid , right ?? I think that maybe the more people that write a 5 Star review for this DVD -- maybe it will be available someday . Can't find anywhere !! Its like one big teeze !! I really want to see Kelly Brook( yes- she is in this so its got to be good ) . I know I could pprobablywatch on youtube but there is no fun in that . I want the real thing !!! So if anyone knows where I could find this DVD -- let me know . Thanks
